{"tid":1440969,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然諗到奇招罷交稅","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T16:31:24.000Z","uid":276754,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68cd99ccf89cbb5353095bc28f77bd23f74963e6","tid":1440969,"uid":276754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"假設我而家去到下次報稅前不斷每星期捐一百蚊比唔同NGO<br />\n草草埋埋十幾張單<br />\n之後2020年報稅唔小心漏報捐款<br />\n等佢一出評稅結果就即刻提出反對評稅<br />\n到再出評稅結果再反對<br />\n每次都劑牙膏式補一張捐款單<br />\n以評局做事效率，分分鐘拖到一年半年<br />\n一個人做尚算搞得掂<br />\n幾萬人做就不得了<br />\n前提係佢容許你暫緩繳稅<br />\n唔係就只能夠拖慢行政效率<br />\n未必可以令政府收唔倒錢<br />\n同埋其實預繳稅應該拖唔倒<br />\n免稅額扣都係扣第二期<br />\n不過個effect最早都要2020年中至尾先見效🤦🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"1a141855d97fe13d5b52958f7f800221cbb60f98","tid":1440969,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"@2225 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPHT1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=9230521e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZcvhiq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZcvhiq.png&h=14f5fc07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},{"pid":"e137fc8b2b8dbdc0b37409e8b20085bf514d8420","tid":1440969,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"講起奇招，我都有計<br />\n【戰略】撳美金現金係最低成本嘅革命手段，成功嘅話無需攬炒，得中共自炒。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/adjxyLU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/adjxyLU</a>"},{"pid":"ad8af05c61591bd63969e9f957d912ab06467ef4","tid":1440969,"uid":276754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"有無稅務朋友解釋下work唔work"},{"pid":"16d1227fa143ccb2d48f73f7d1c48060a173dcc4","tid":1